to the Whole, by Unifying the Thought with the Heart, is the Genuine Worship. And 
this is the Consciousness which conveys the Human Being from the Status of Godness 
to the Status of being a Servant of God. Here, there is Love without expectation, 
Giving without Receiving and Serving the Total. This is the Highest Degree Humanity 
can attain. 



