When Your Cerebral Energies take the Light Years under Supervision, You can 
even create Universes. And You can become the LORD of the Order You have 
established. But You are always obliged to serve under the Supervision of the Divine 
Plan. 

The Divine Plan is a Hierarchical Order of the Lordly Energies who had been 
